author: kdy1
message:
Update `swc_core` to `v16.10.0` (#77489)

### What?

Update `swc_core`.

ChangeLog: https://github.com/swc-project/swc/compare/swc_core%40v16.9.0...swc_core%40v16.10.0

### Why?

To make the SWC minifier faster
